        <Parent_String>bone and bone components materials [300387684], combination inorganic/organic animal material [300206572], combination inorganic/organic material [300206579], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
